### Read all films
GET http://localhost:3000/films

### Read filtered films
GET http://localhost:3000/films?minimum-duration=130

### Read one film
GET http://localhost:3000/films/1

### Create film
POST http://localhost:3000/films
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "The Dark Knight",
    "director": "Christopher Nolan",
    "duration": 152,
    "budget": 185
}

### Test invalid duration
POST http://localhost:3000/films
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test",
    "director": "Test",
    "duration": -1
}

### Test DELETE
DELETE http://localhost:3000/films/1

### Test PATCH (mise à jour partielle)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/films/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "duration": 190,
    "budget": 200
}

### Test PUT (mise à jour complète)
PUT http://localhost:3000/films/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Inception Updated",
    "director": "Christopher Nolan",
    "duration": 148,
    "budget": 160,
    "description": "Updated description",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/inception.jpg"
}

### Test PUT (création avec ID spécifique)
